Hi, this is a simple tune converting software.
It is write in python2.7 with a Qt4 GUI.

How to use?
Simply! Copy yor song, select the new tone and convert it!

As you can see, you can read your song in the browser and you can save it.

In the file menu there are some preferences.

You can convert notation. italian <=> english
You can convert notes. sharp <=> flat

